Please join us on 04/30 evening to talk about interesting question. Dolly will be our host.<br />Session 1：<br />Refernece：<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/UuU8gi7U0x4">https://youtu.be/UuU8gi7U0x4</a><!-- m --><br />Question:<br />1.Do you usually talk to yourself?<br />2.What does a typical day for your future self look like?<br />3.Do you think build good study habits is major coming true the dream.<br /><br />Agenda：<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />Session 2<br />If you could choose a brand new name for yourself, what would it be?<br /><br />Question:<br />1.Before you change your name, what should you think about more.<br />2.Did your old classmates change their names after graduation ten years later ?<br />3.Do you like your name a lot?<br />4.Do you have nickname when you was a student or on the job?<br /><br />Agenda：<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:35 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">dora</a> — Tue Apr 25, 2023 9:00 am — Replies 0 — Views 12</p><hr />
